# Railway Configuration

## Environment Variables Required

## Services Configuration

{
  "services": {
    "evofit-backend": {
      "type": "app",
      "root": "backend",
      "build": {
        "commands": {
          "build": "npm run build",
          "start": "npm start"
        }
      }
    },
    "evofit-db": {
      "type": "postgres",
      "version": "16.x",
      "ipAllowlist": ["0.0.0.0/0"]
    },
    "evofit-redis": {
      "type": "redis",
      "version": "7.x"
    }
  }
}
